Enhancements to SkyPi (in no particular order)
==============================================

1. Add command line options for:
   a) System time / DS1307 support on uLCD
   b) Latitude & Longitude
   c) Display sleep times and nap blanking
   d) Cuckoo enable/disable
   e) Star database location, constellation lines

2. Add UI for setting lat/long, other options

3. View window and direction

4. [Optional] Use X11 display via Qt
